                    <div class="cols-3-big">
                        <img src="roseGarden.png"> 
                        <h3> Rose Garden </h3>
                        <p> Named after India's former president, Zakir Hussain and created in 1967 under the guidance of Dr Dr M.S. Randhawa, Chandigarh's first chief commissioner, the garden has the distinction of being Asia's largest. The garden has not only roses, but also trees of medicinal value. </p>
                    </div>
