                        <img src="sukhnaLake.png"> 
                        <h3> Sukhna Lake </h3>
                        <p> The lake, which was the venue for the Asian Rowing Championships, has the longest channel for rowing and yachting events in Asia. Sukhna is a sanctuary for many exotic migratory birds like the Siberian duck, storks and cranes, during the winter months.</p>  
                    </div>    
