                        <img src="thunderZone.jpg"> 
                        <h3> Thunder Zone </h3>
                        <p> Splash through water, as you come zipping down the waterslides and land face first in crystal clear pool of water and emerge spluttering out, grinning ear to ear at Thunderzone in Chandigarh, an amusement cum waterpark.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cols-3">  
                        <img src="leisureValley.jpg"> 
                        <h3> Leisure Valley </h3>
                        <p> Leisure Valley Chandigarh, is a continuum of several theme gardens that attract people from all walks of life to come and soak in the good vibes and breathe in the fresh air.</p>
